scenes.title: [VR] Top Class Girls Who Visit My House of Erotic Books - Sumire, Ichika, Hinako
scenes.synopsis: I'm known as the “Cheeky Cow Yinka”, a person who doesn't stand out in class and is a member of the lower caste. However, I'm confident that my knowledge of anime and manga, especially erotic books and doujinshi, is second to none. In my fantasies, I make the girls at the top of the caste in my class “hiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiii” over and over again. But one day, while I was reading a new doujinshi behind my back at school, I was discovered by a group of girls from the top caste. I couldn't compete with the beautiful girls I was talking to for the first time, so I had to “show them other doujinshis at my house”... I didn't know if those beautiful girls were interested in erotic books.... But it was the first time for me to have girls come to my house... I was so nervous and waiting for them to come to my house... 3 girls came to my house...
